for e.g for the  adapter config below , target would be 02.
&lt;configs&gt;
  &lt;config name="02"&gt;
    &lt;target&gt;172.19.224.103&lt;/target&gt;
    &lt;user-name&gt;root&lt;/user-name&gt;
